sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>x_matsa_yare_project_task_time_worked</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Update Project Hours</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {
	
	// Get all Time Worked Records
	var total = 0;
	var timeWorked = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_yare_project_task_time_worked');
	timeWorked.addEncodedQuery("client_project="+current.getValue('client_project'));
	timeWorked.query();
	
	// Total up all the timw worked records
	while (timeWorked.next()) {
		total+=timeWorked.hours;
	}
	
	// Update Remaing Balance
	var projectRec = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_yare_client_project');
	if(projectRec.get(current.getValue('client_project'))){
		
		// Update Project Hours Spent
		projectRec.project_hours_spent = total;
		
		// Get difference between hours and hours spent
		var startingHours = 0;
		if(projectRec.total_project_hours)
			startingHours = projectRec.total_project_hours;
		var timeRemaining = startingHours - projectRec.project_hours_spent;
		
		// Update time remaining with difference
		projectRec.project_hours_remaining = timeRemaining;
		
		// submit updates
		projectRec.update();
	}
	
})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>brent.llewellyn</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-09-06 13:58:18</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>12f1d0c3db18ab005dbe38f0ad9619b5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>6</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Update Project Hours</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="yare" source="x_matsa_yare">8307866adbd86b005dbe38f0ad96197c</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="yare">8307866adbd86b005dbe38f0ad96197c</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_12f1d0c3db18ab005dbe38f0ad9619b5</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>brent.llewellyn</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-09-06 14:08:59</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=12f1d0c3db18ab005dbe38f0ad9619b5"/></record_update>
